### Phase 4 — Evaluation & Comparison

#### [NEW] [src/evaluation.py](file:///d:/EcoToxAI/src/evaluation.py)

**Metrics computed for each model:**

| Metric | What It Measures |
|---|---|
| **R² Score** | How much variance is explained (closer to 1 = better) |
| **RMSE** | Root Mean Squared Error (lower = better) |
| **MAE** | Mean Absolute Error (lower = better) |
| **MAPE** | Mean Absolute Percentage Error |
| **10-Fold CV R²** | Cross-validated R² for robustness |

**Outputs generated:**
- Model comparison bar chart (R², RMSE, MAE side by side)
- Predicted vs. Actual scatter plot for each model
- Residual distribution plots
- Learning curves (train vs. validation error)
- CSV report with all metrics for all models

#### [NEW] [src/explainability.py](file:///d:/EcoToxAI/src/explainability.py)
- **SHAP values** for tree-based models (which descriptors drive toxicity?)
- **Feature importance** rankings from Random Forest and XGBoost
- **Permutation importance** for model-agnostic feature ranking

