### Phase 5 — Master Training Script

#### [NEW] [train.py](file:///d:/EcoToxAI/train.py)
Single entry point that:
1. Loads and preprocesses data
2. Trains all 7 models with hyperparameter tuning
3. Evaluates all models with 10-fold CV
4. Builds ensemble from top 3 performers
5. Generates comparison plots and reports
6. Saves the best model + ensemble to `outputs/models/`
7. Prints a summary leaderboard to console

