### Phase 6 — Prediction Pipeline

#### [NEW] [src/predict.py](file:///d:/EcoToxAI/src/predict.py)
- Load saved best model (or ensemble)
- Accept new molecular descriptors as input
- Return predicted LC50 value + confidence interval
- Classify toxicity level:
  - **Very High Toxicity**: LC50 < 1 mg/L
  - **High Toxicity**: 1–10 mg/L
  - **Moderate Toxicity**: 10–100 mg/L
  - **Low Toxicity**: > 100 mg/L
- (Following EPA GHS classification for aquatic acute toxicity)

