### How to Get the Data

1. Go to **https://archive.ics.uci.edu/dataset/504/qsar+fish+toxicity**
2. Click the **"Download"** button
3. Extract the CSV file
4. Place it as `d:\EcoToxAI\data\qsar_fish_toxicity.csv`

> [!TIP]
> Alternatively, we can download it programmatically using the `ucimlrepo` Python package during training — no manual download needed.

