### Manual Verification
- Review model comparison charts in `outputs/plots/`
- Verify predictions match expected toxicity ranges for known compounds
- Test the web interface for usability and visual quality
- Compare ensemble predictions against individual model predictions

### Success Criteria
| Metric | Minimum Target | Good Target |
|---|---|---|
| Best Single Model R² | > 0.55 | > 0.65 |
| Ensemble R² | > 0.60 | > 0.70 |
| RMSE | < 1.2 | < 0.9 |
